        <h3>Inventory Health</h3>
        <p>On-hand levels, low stock alerts, and turnover performance.</p>
        <p><strong>Key focus:</strong> Inventory On Hand, Reorder Alerts.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Customer Insights</h3>
        <p>VIP customers, loyalty engagement, and retention trends.</p>
        <p><strong>Key focus:</strong> Top Customers, Retention Report.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Team Performance</h3>
        <p>Sales by employee, transaction audits, and labor productivity.</p>
        <p><strong>Key focus:</strong> Sales by Employee, Shift Productivity.</p>
    </div>
</div>
